003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eDevice\u003c/strong\u003e: \u003ca href=\"https://github.com/unkyulee/micro-journal\" rel=\"ugc\"\u003eMicro Journal\u003c/a\u003e - Above version is a \u003ca href=\"https://github.com/unkyulee/micro-journal/tree/main/micro-journal-rev-2-revamp\" rel=\"ugc\"\u003eRev.2\u003c/a\u003e by Un Kyu Lee\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHardware\u003c/strong\u003e: Raspberry Pi Zero 2W\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eKeyboard\u003c/strong\u003e: 48-key ortholinear mini keyboard with side knobs for scrolling\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eSwitches\u003c/strong\u003e: \u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.de/dp/B0BM9KR6QH\" rel=\"ugc\"\u003eAkko V3 Pro Creamy Blue\u003c/a\u003e (clicky)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eKeycaps\u003c/strong\u003e: \u003ca href=\"https://oblotzky.industries/products/kam-playground\" rel=\"ugc\"\u003eKAM Playground\u003c/a\u003e by Oblotzky Industries (KAM uniform spherical profile)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eKeymap Firmware\u003c/strong\u003e: \u003ca href=\"https://qmk.fm/\" rel=\"ugc\"\u003eQMK\u003c/a\u003e / \u003ca href=\"https://get.vial.today/\" rel=\"ugc\"\u003eVial\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eBattery\u003c/strong\u003e: Molicel INR 18650 Li-ion\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eOS\u003c/strong\u003e: Debian/Raspberry Pi OS based\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eWord Processor (Editor)\u003c/strong\u003e: \u003ca href=\"https://neovim.io/\" rel=\"ugc\"\u003eNeovim\u003c/a\u003e configured as a word processor (Vim Motions, themes, split screen, fuzzy find, Markdown rendering, \u003ccode\u003e[[wikilink]]\u003c/code\u003e support)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eFile Manager\u003c/strong\u003e: \u003ca href=\"https://github.com/sxyazi/yazi\" rel=\"ugc\"\u003eYazi\u003c/a\u003e (Rust-based, replaces Ranger)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eVersion Control\u003c/strong\u003e: \u003ca href=\"https://git-scm.com/\" rel=\"ugc\"\u003eGit\u003c/a\u003e — syncs Markdown writing between device and laptop\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n","description_plain":"- **Device**: [Micro Journal](https://github.com/unkyulee/micro-journal) - Above version is a [Rev.2](https://github.com/unkyulee/micro-journal/tree/main/micro-journal-rev-2-revamp) by Un Kyu Lee\r\n- **Hardware**: Raspberry Pi Zero 2W\r\n- **Keyboard**: 48-key ortholinear mini keyboard with side knobs for scrolling\r\n- **Switches**: [Akko V3 Pro Creamy Blue](https://www.amazon.de/dp/B0BM9KR6QH) (clicky)\r\n- **Keycaps**: [KAM Playground](https://oblotzky.industries/products/kam-playground) by Oblotzky Industries (KAM uniform spherical profile)\r\n- **Keymap Firmware**: [QMK](https://qmk.fm/) / [Vial](https://get.vial.today/)\r\n- **Battery**: Molicel INR 18650 Li-ion\r\n- **OS**: Debian/Raspberry Pi OS based\r\n- **Word Processor (Editor)**: [Neovim](https://neovim.io/) configured as a word processor (Vim Motions, themes, split screen, fuzzy find, Markdown rendering, `[[wikilink]]` support)\r\n- **File Manager**: [Yazi](https://github.com/sxyazi/yazi) (Rust-based, replaces Ranger)\r\n- **Version Control**: [Git](https://git-scm.com/) — syncs Markdown writing between device and laptop","submitter_user":"sspaeti","user_is_author":true,"tags":["hardware"],"short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/he46nq","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/he46nq/distraction_free_writing_with_micro"},{"short_id":"ucp0wf","created_at":"2026-03-27T08:03:06.000-05:00","title":"What are you doing this weekend?","url":"","score":5,"flags":0,"comment_count":9,"description":"\u003cp\u003eFeel free to tell what you plan on doing this weekend and even ask for help or feedback.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePlease keep in mind it’s more than OK to do nothing at all too!\u003c/p\u003e\n","description_plain":"Feel free to tell what you plan on doing this weekend and